{
  "text": "We are going to use some particular cases in which the tobacco industry has responded to attempts by both governmental Administrations in the US and several civil associations to support new forms of regulation (see [CITATION_1] . Our application of Grice's model will point precisely to these cases.",
  "correct_citation": {
